&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Sedulous Subversion SUCKS!&amp;nbsp; I have to keep going back and forth during battle AND during raid recovery I can barely even ask to go use the restroom because I'm supposed to be feeding the healers.....&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;PLEASE find an alternative way to have the utility of twitch in the game while removing it from us.&amp;nbsp; Merely adding a way for the effect to be in game without removing it from our spellbooks won't be enough, because as long as we have that ridiculous spell in our repertoire it's going to be asked for.&amp;nbsp; REMOVE TWITCH!&amp;nbsp; Find a way to put it in their hands...PLEASE!&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
